<BR>
tato vajraśiṣyāṃ praveśayedanena vidhinā svayaṃ vajrācāryo vajrakodhatirintirimudrāṃ badhvā, śiṣyāya bandhayedanena hṛdayena oṃ gṛṇha vajra samaya huṃ vaṃ //<BR>
