<BR>
tataḥ samāviśati / tenāveśena sarvatathāgatairadhiṣṭhyate / sarvaṃ cātītānāgatapratyutpannannimiṣādeva jānāti / avadhyaśca bhavati sarvasatvebhyaḥ, adhṛṣyaḥ / huṃkāreṇa ca sarvasatvanigrahānugrahasamarthībhavati / vajrapāṇiścāsya nityaṃ sarvakāryāṇi sādhayatīti //<BR>
<BR>
