vajrabandhaṃ dṛḍhīkṛtya kaniṣṭhā padmasaṃyutā /<BR>
kuñcitā[gryaṃ pīḍayantu] dvayaṅguṣṭhakavacīkṛte- // ti // 13 //<BR>
sā evāṅguṣṭhadaṃṣṭrā tu samāṅguṣṭhapraveśitā /<BR>
ataḥ paraṃ pravakṣyāmi samayāgryo niruttarāḥ // 14 //<BR>
