tathaiva vajrabandhe tu tarjanī padmasandhitā /<BR>
aṅguṣṭhā bandhaparyaṅkā madhyasaṃkocavigrahā // 19 //<BR>
tathaiva vajrabandhe tu vajramaṅguṣṭhasandhitā /<BR>
