vajraratnaṃ svamuṣṇīṣe bhāvayaṃ susamāhitaḥ /<BR>
badhvā vai karmamudrāṃ tu bhavedrājā sukarmakṛd // iti // 4 //<BR>
<BR>
athāsāṃ hṛdayāni bhavanti /<BR>
oṃ vajraratnahṛdayābhiṣiñca hoḥ //<BR>
