bhāvayetsatvavajrāṃ tu samayānāṃ bhavetpatiḥ // 2 //<BR>
paṭādiṣu samālikhya vajraratnaṃ svamātmanā /<BR>
bhāvayaṃ dhyānamudrāṃ tu bhave[ddharmapatirdhruvaṃ] // 3 //<BR>
paṭādiṣu samālikhya vajraratnamanuttaraṃ /<BR>
bhāvayetkarmamudrāṃ tu bhavetkarmādhipaḥ svayam // iti // // 4 //<BR>
<BR>
tatraiṣāṃ hṛdayāni bhavanti /<BR>
vajraratna[bimbādhitiṣṭha] //<BR>
vajraratnabimba pratiṣṭha //<BR>
vajraratnabimbāviśa //<BR>
vajraratnabimba kuru //<BR>
<BR>
