svamukhe caiva prakṣipya bhavedvācāṃ patistu saḥ // 3 //<BR>
sauvarṇamanyaratnaṃ vā vajraratnantu bhāvayet /<BR>
uṣṇīṣe bhāvayaṃ bhūyo sarvakarmapatirbhaved // iti // 4 //<BR>
<BR>
tatraiṣāṃ hṛdayāni bhavanti /<BR>
oṃ vajraratnahṛdayābharaṇa hūṃ //<BR>
oṃ vajraratnābhiṣeka mahārthaprada //<BR>
oṃ vajraratnavācaspate //<BR>
oṃ vajraratnamahākarmapate //<BR>
<BR>
tato maṇikulasamayamudrārahasyajñānaṃ śikṣayet /<BR>
<BR>
mahāvajramaṇiṃ badhvā tanmaṇiṃ strībhage tathā /<BR>
